&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Increased efficiency and productivity&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Initial setup costs can be high&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Reduction in human error&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;May require ongoing maintenance&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Scalability of operations&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Potential job displacement concerns&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Ability to analyze large data sets&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Dependence on technology and data quality&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
