&lt;h2 id="workflow-of-ai-automation-implementation"&gt;Workflow of AI Automation Implementation&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;To ensure a successful AI automation implementation, businesses should follow a structured workflow. Here’s a simple representation of the process:&lt;/p&gt;
