&lt;h3 id="4-zapier"&gt;4. Zapier&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Zapier is a powerful automation tool that connects different applications to automate workflows. By setting up “Zaps,” users can trigger actions in one app based on events in another.&lt;/p&gt;
